{"type": "article", "id": 49135, "title": "“世界上最适合孩子的 SUV”，纸板做的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-11T23:49:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 46998, "name": "Muka Design Lab"}, {"id": 46999, "name": "Mindo"}, {"id": 47000, "name": "Studio Anansi"}, {"id": 47001, "name": "Lazerian"}, {"id": 47002, "name": "Skoda"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}, {"id": 47003, "name": "Parse/Error"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180112074809P1zK8XtHqQyLlprE.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; background-color: #ffffff} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333; background-color: #ffffff} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Earthquake Lamp by Parse/Error </h3><p>法国马赛艺术家 Parse/Error 生活在东京，2011 年的日本大地震给予他启发，设计出这款地震灯，能够实时响应来自世界各地的地震信息。他找到地震研究机构 IRIS，将实时数据关联在灯体上，延迟几分钟后，地震灯便能响应。</p><p>长长的灯轴代表着经度轴，光脉冲和声脉冲根据地震的位置和震级大小而变化，甚至发出令人不安的隆隆声。Parse/Error 试图以这种形式邀请人们观察一个活跃的地球不断运动的现状。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801112327199k603pl4b7THzPVZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232719cu2IRyzPO0NQVXb9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232720ZCxwWbi8H1g27ohX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232720hTA3LSoVzBePO2MQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232720MrkusxT6BPej3JW8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232721fimvCGlUd3JsSRj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Skoda cardboard Karoq car by Lazerian</h3><p>捷克汽车制造商斯柯达为了庆祝 KAROQ SUV 车型的发布，它们创造了一款用纸板制造的“世界上最适合孩子的 SUV”。这辆纸板车由专业从事纸板设计的英国设计工作室 Lazerian 操刀，花费了 10 周时间精心制作，尺寸与 KAROQ SUV 车身完全相同。</p><p>根据 1000 名 11 岁以下的儿童的问卷调查显示，他们希望装进一台 SUV 的东西包括游戏控制台、触摸屏、海洋球、扬声器和 WiFi 等等。在调查中投票最多的是音乐播放和电影播放选项。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=c0531obmbqd&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232804czNVUWCm7j0Hgbid.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232805mC10TsUw5Ztzg2Br.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647922\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232805YM4kO7ECfZqRhQDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232805Qf3BrnVvLtGEu2RY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232806HeMdlT7O46wrDazo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232818WMcY1yI0HsZOTkeq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Penguin Huddle by Jasper Morrison</h3><p>企鹅出版社最近邀请英国工业设计师 Jasper Morrison，设计了一款可调节书立，将在本月的巴黎家居装饰博览会上亮相。企鹅提出的要求是要创造一个全新的书籍集合地，Jasper Morrison 延续了他一贯以来注重简约和功能性的风格，用两端折叠铝合金板材料，置入一个滑动装置即可。它可以容纳大约 18 至 27 本书，包括各种尺寸的平装书。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232903sAPOyJYmbXwR7d6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232904ny3LkfarXNAOwiJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232907YTh5tRKIbwzqCJoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232907OVP5kW0Ee6QBlm2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232911cnxkPFBuCeq1fTrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Tulum Collection by Studio Anansi </h3><p>Tulum 不算是墨西哥人气极高的玛雅遗址游览地，但因为地处加勒比海海岸，使它成为一处热门旅游地点。设计工作室 Anansi 以 Tulum 为灵感，创造了一系列彩色瓷砖，图案分为 Trio 和 Box Grid 两类，每一类都由三种充满活力的色彩定义，意在创造热带风情的味道。</p><p>因其图案的特殊性，瓷砖可以以各种方式排列，混搭色彩，制造个性拼贴样式。这些 20*20 厘米的水泥砖皆是在墨西哥手工制作而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232936U6RKnFdAvOYJDGZB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.531250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801112329369IHUE4pr7mXsjYnv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232936OTigPxaHsBJr7hKc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111232938ca18ATPRHQ3qhZmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Murcia Outdoor Collection by Muka for Mindo</h3><p>西班牙设计工作室 Muka Design Lab 为美国家具品牌 Mindo 设计了一系列新的户外家具 Murcia。</p><p>喷涂饰面的铝制框架被编织绳缠绕，既创造了通风透气的功能，适用于炎热的热带地区，又加入了编织软垫，为每个座位增添舒适性。Murcia 系列包括沙发、可调节躺椅、咖啡桌和边桌。蓝灰色调与海边风景很搭。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233123CvG2k8L56DtxPH0A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.210938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801112330028AHD3miwU7VQoEyv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233004sH6M2VDiUhI8LWam.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233018TCqkLSsrahBvx5VK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233029ME2t3j6QihoYlCPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Open Vessel Meditation Pods </h3><p>我们都知道，每天坐在电脑前数小时会有多乏味。但好消息是，为了提高员工的工作效率和幸福感，越来越多公司在尝试与工作中的倦怠情绪作斗争，Open Vessel 是一种解决方案。</p><p>它是一个冥想吊舱，希望通过提供一个舒适的茧形半封闭空间，切断你与周边工作环境的联系，暂享独处氛围，内置的平板电脑设置，集合了各种与艺术家合作创作的原创音乐，员工可以放松在里面听听歌，沉默静坐，甚至是做个白日梦。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233153MwyBrmWRhAsGJbEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233154rfIsD9UjFRmKYeAx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233154UvCgRVEmSPDZj2nT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233156ptjBcLW8GlE6rb03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233156o4kj79NKdn3RuyBJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180111233158p4i6tcx2UMhLbnjw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}